nodes.text: A clone who served as a shock trooper with the Coruscant Guard accompanied Commander Stone and several other troopers of the Diplomatic Escort Group with Senator Kharrus and Representative Jar Jar Binks to Florrum.

He survived the crash of their shuttle after which he attempted to repair the shuttle's homing beacon but was unsuccessful. He along with all other clones survived the mission and departed Florrum aboard the Twilight.
